## About AQUA THERM Praha

AQUA THERM Praha is the 26th International Trade Fair for Heating, Ventilation, Air Conditioning, Measuring, Regulation, Sanitary and Ecological Technology. As one of Central Europe's leading HVAC exhibitions, it attracts industry professionals from across the region.

## Exhibition Sectors

Heating Systems | Ventilation & Air Conditioning | Sanitary Technology | Measuring & Regulation | Renewable Energy | Building Automation

## Event Scale

**600+ Exhibitors** and **15,000+ Visitors** make AQUA THERM Praha the key marketplace for HVAC and building technology in the Czech Republic and Central Europe.

## Why Attend

Discover latest HVAC innovations, source equipment and systems, connect with contractors and engineers, and access the Central European building technology market.
